">Tặng Lý Bạch (Thu lai tương cố thượng phiêu bồng) - 贈李白（秋來相顧尚飄蓬）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/T%C3%A2y-S%C6%A1n-thi-ho%E1%BA%A1-gi%E1%BA%A3-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-d%C6%B0-nh%C3%A2n-t%C3%A1i-d%E1%BB%A5ng-ti%E1%BB%81n-v%E1%BA%ADn-vi-t%E1%BA%A1/poem-sTETKXl0tUNMHQSfVPqeGQ">Tây Sơn thi hoạ giả tam thập dư nhân, tái dụng tiền vận vi tạ - 西山詩和者三十餘人，再用前韻為謝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Vi-n%C3%B4ng/poem-Ku5WpLUumKKL1PPkzQ2vXQ">Vi nông - 為農</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ph%C3%BA-L%E1%BB%99c-b%C3%A1t-c%E1%BA%A3nh-k%E1%BB%B3-4-Thu%C3%BD-V%C3%A2n-s%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-8qhmweDwZmfxajMMGxuH3w">Vịnh Phú Lộc bát cảnh kỳ 4 - Thuý Vân sơn tự - 詠富祿八景其四－翠雲山寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-k%E1%BB%B9-Kim-L%C4%83ng-t%E1%BB%AD-tr%C3%ACnh-L%C6%B0-l%E1%BB%A5c-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-IByNfF3hXSLnQNyGLAc14A">Xuất kỹ Kim Lăng tử trình Lư lục kỳ 4 - 出妓金陵子呈盧六其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br></div>	</div>
